Berlusconi to Meet ECB’s Bini Smaghi Today, Ansa Says

-- B y   J e f f r e y   D o n o v a n   a n d   C h i a r a   V a s a r r i
-- 
2011-10-14T14:16:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/berlusconi-to-meet-ecb-s-bini-smaghi-today-ansa-says.html
Italian Prime Minister  Silvio
Berlusconi  will meet today in  Rome  with European Central Bank
Executive Board member Lorenzo Bini Smaghi, Ansa newswire
reported, citing lawmakers.  Berlusconi earlier told reporters that he would discuss the
Bank of  Italy ’s future leader in talks with President Giorgio
Napolitano today, pledging to nominate a successor to Governor
 Mario Draghi  by Nov. 1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Jeffrey Donovan  at 
 jdonovan26@bloomberg.net  